  "instructions": [
    "Heat a dry wok over medium heat until shimmering.",
    "Add olive oil and swirl to coat the pan.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic, sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika and wok-hei seasoning, cook for 30 seconds.",
    "Add cherry tomato halves, cook until they start to soften.",
    "Reduce heat to low, stir in spinach and olives, cover briefly until spinach wilts.",
    "Fold in crumbled feta and toasted almonds, cook for 2 minutes, allowing flavors to mingle.",
    "Drizzle lemon juice and season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot, topped with a generous handful of toffee popcorn."
  ],
